text: Javier Viñolas (born 11 March 1971) is a Spanish rowing coxswain. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
